tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE PatientFeedback (
  feedback_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id UUID,
  survey_id UUID,
  feedback_text TEXT,
  feedback_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE survey_responses (
    response_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    survey_id INT,
    response_text TEXT,
    response_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE responses (
  response_id INT,
  patient_id INT,
  survey_id INT,
  response_text TEXT,
  response_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE responses (
    response_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    survey_id INT,
    patient_id INT,
    response_text TEXT,
    response_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE surveys (
  survey_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id UUID,
  provider_id UUID,
  feedback_text TEXT,
  survey_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE patients (
  patient_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_name TEXT,
  date_of_birth DATE,
  gender TEXT,
  address TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE providers (
  provider_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  provider_name TEXT,
  specialty TEXT,
  location TEXT,
  contact_number TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE responses (
  response_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  survey_id UUID,
  patient_id UUID,
  provider_id UUID,
  question_id UUID,
  response_text TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE questions (
  question_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  question_text TEXT,
  question_type TEXT,
  survey_id UUID
)
